ns drink it.\r\n\r\n582\r\n00:41:11,152 --> 00:41:14,227\r\nThis ought to take the sting\r\nout of being occupied.\r\n\r\n583\r\n00:41:14,507 --> 00:41:15,625\r\nYou said it.\r\n\r\n584\r\n00:41:15,866 --> 00:41:17,902\r\nHere's Iooking at you, kid.\r\n\r\n585\r\n00:41:24,295 --> 00:41:26,611\r\n(GESTAPO OFFICER IN GERMAN\r\nOVER SPEAKERS)\r\n\r\n586\r\n00:41:44,028 --> 00:41:45,747\r\nMy German's a Iittle rusty.\r\n\r\n587\r\n00:41:46,986 --> 00:41:48,544\r\nIt's the Gestapo.\r\n\r\n588\r\n00:41:50,381 --> 00:41:53,027\r\nThey say they expect\r\nto be in Paris tomorrow.\r\n\r\n589\r\n00:41:54,190 --> 00:41:57,556\r\nThey're telIing us how to act\r\nwhen they come marching in.\r\n\r\n590\r\n00:42:00,685 --> 00:42:03,529\r\nWith the world crumbling,\r\nwe pick this time to fall in love.\r\n\r\n591\r\n00:42:03,772 --> 00:42:05,414\r\nYeah, it's pretty bad timing.\r\n\r\n592\r\n00:42:05,655 --> 00:42:07,418\r\nWhere were you ten years ago?\r\n\r\n593\r\n00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:09,062\r\nTen years ago?\r\n\r\n594\r\n00:42:10,667 --> 00:42:11,988\r\nLet's see....\r\n\r\n595\r\n00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:15,956\r\nYes, l was having a brace\r\nput on my teeth. Where were you?\r\n\r\n596\r\n00:42:16,599 --> 00:42:18,323\r\nLooking for a job.\r\n\r\n597\r\n00:42:20,207 --> 00:42:22,572\r\n(CANNONS FIRE)\r\n\r\n598\r\n00:42:24,415 --> 00:42:25,980\r\nWas that cannon fire?\r\n\r\n599\r\n00:42:26,941 --> 00:42:28,264\r\nOr my heart pounding?\r\n\r\n600\r\n00:42:28,506 --> 00:42:33,355\r\nIt's the German 77th, and judging\r\nby the sound, onIy about 35 miles away.\r\n\r\n601\r\n00:42:34,640 --> 00:42:36,723\r\nAnd getting closer every minute.\r\n\r\n602\r\n00:42:37,807 --> 00:42:41,332\r\nHere, here, drink up.\r\nWe'll never finish the other three.\r\n\r\n603\r\n00:42:41,575 --> 00:42:45,462\r\nGermans wilI be here pretty soon\r\nand they'Il come looking for you.\r\n\r\n604\r\n00:42:45,664 --> 00:42:46,986\r\nThere's a price on your head.\r\n\r\n605\r\n00:42:47,227 --> 00:42:50,153\r