16 --> 01:33:12,689\r\nI've got a job to do too.\r\n\r\n1442\r\n01:33:12,889 --> 01:33:16,235\r\nWhere l go, you can't folIow.\r\nWhat l do, you can't be any part of.\r\n\r\n1443\r\n01:33:16,914 --> 01:33:18,428\r\nI'm no good at being noble.\r\n\r\n1444\r\n01:33:18,669 --> 01:33:21,617\r\nBut it doesn't take much to see\r\nthat the problems of three people...\r\n\r\n1445\r\n01:33:21,816 --> 01:33:24,565\r\n...don't amount to a hill of beans\r\nin this crazy worId.\r\n\r\n1446\r\n01:33:24,766 --> 01:33:26,797\r\nSomeday you'll understand that.\r\n\r\n1447\r\n01:33:31,660 --> 01:33:33,653\r\nHere's Iooking at you, kid.\r\n\r\n1448\r\n01:33:48,317 --> 01:33:50,590\r\n-Everything is in order.\r\nRICK: All except one thing.\r\n\r\n1449\r\n01:33:50,789 --> 01:33:52,820\r\nThere's something you shouId know.\r\n\r\n1450\r\n01:33:53,021 --> 01:33:54,695\r\nI don't ask you\r\nto explain anything.\r\n\r\n1451\r\n01:33:54,894 --> 01:33:57,404\r\nIt may make a difference\r\nto you Iater on.\r\n\r\n1452\r\n01:33:57,684 --> 01:33:59,755\r\nYou said you knew about IIsa and me.\r\n\r\n1453\r\n01:34:00,075 --> 01:34:02,505\r\nShe was at my place\r\nlast night when you were.\r\n\r\n1454\r\n01:34:02,745 --> 01:34:05,255\r\nShe came there for the letters.\r\nIsn't that true?\r\n\r\n1455\r\n01:34:06,372 --> 01:34:07,328\r\nYes.\r\n\r\n1456\r\n01:34:08,045 --> 01:34:09,879\r\nShe tried everything.\r\nNothing worked.\r\n\r\n1457\r\n01:34:10,159 --> 01:34:13,664\r\nShe did her best to convince me\r\nthat she was still in love with me.\r\n\r\n1458\r\n01:34:13,865 --> 01:34:16,214\r\nBut that was aIl over Iong ago.\r\n\r\n1459\r\n01:34:16,415 --> 01:34:19,243\r\nFor your sake, she pretended it wasn't.\r\nI let her pretend.\r\n\r\n1460\r\n01:34:20,281 --> 01:34:21,276\r\nI understand.\r\n\r\n1461\r\n01:34:21,596 --> 01:34:23,668\r\n-Here it is.\r\n-Thanks.\r\n\r\n1462\r\n01:34:24,385 --> 01:34:25,939\r\nI appreciate it.\r\n\r\n1463\r\n01:34:27,015 --> 01:34:28,610\r\nWelcome back to the fight