olor=\"#808080\">(NAGIN ON TV)</font> We are facing a\r\nstorm that most of us have feared.</i>\r\n\r\n404\r\n00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:45,571\r\n<i>The storm is now a category five</i>\r\n\r\n405\r\n00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:48,730\r\n<i>with sustained winds\r\nof 150 miles an hour</i>\r\n\r\n406\r\n00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:53,170\r\n<i>with wind gusts\r\nof 190 miles per hour.</i>\r\n\r\n407\r\n00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:06,164\r\n<i><font color=\"#804040\">JOE</font>: I will get out.</i>\r\n\r\n408\r\n00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:09,567\r\n<i>And whoever you are,</i>\r\n\r\n409\r\n00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:12,525\r\n<i>wherever you are,</i>\r\n\r\n410\r\n00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,969\r\n<i>I will find you.</i>\r\n\r\n411\r\n00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:24,045\r\n<i>Preserve, protect and defend.</i>\r\n\r\n412\r\n00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:26,242\r\n<i><font color=\"#804040\">MAN</font>: The Constitution\r\nof the United States.</i>\r\n\r\n413\r\n00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:28,050\r\n<i>The Constitution\r\nof the United States.</i>\r\n\r\n414\r\n00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,481\r\n<i>So help you God.\r\nSo help me God.</i>\r\n\r\n415\r\n00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:40,721\r\n<font color=\"#804040\">WOMAN</font>: <i>Freedom is yours.\r\nYou can do it.</i>\r\n\r\n416\r\n00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:45,164\r\n<i>Keep pushing, keep breathing.\r\nFeel the inner peace within you.</i>\r\n\r\n417\r\n00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:46,930\r\n<i>Another chance to freedom.</i>\r\n\r\n418\r\n00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:49,202\r\n<i>It's always there for you.</i>\r\n\r\n419\r\n00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,963\r\n<i><font color=\"#804040\">TV REPORTER</font>: That's everything.\r\nBack to you, Ray.</i>\r\n\r\n420\r\n00:27:53,120 --> 00:27:54,451\r\nNinety-one, 92,\r\n\r\n421\r\n00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:56,165\r\n93,\r\n\r\n422\r\n00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,811\r\n94.\r\n\r\n423\r\n00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:02,368\r\n<i>\"<font color=\"#804040\">JOE</font>: \" Dear daughter, today\r\nI leave this place,</i>\r\n\r\n424\r\n00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,081\