on't you have to feed him at 6:00?\r\n- Uh-huh.\r\n\r\n805\r\n02:15:27,653 --> 02:15:29,070\r\nCome in.\r\n\r\n806\r\n02:15:30,781 --> 02:15:34,367\r\n- Oh, here he is now.\r\n- That's my son.\r\n\r\n807\r\n02:15:34,535 --> 02:15:38,496\r\nThat's my son. Oh, oh.\r\n\r\n808\r\n02:15:40,666 --> 02:15:46,294\r\nThat's my son. That's my son!\r\nHa-ha-ha.\r\n\r\n809\r\n02:15:46,462 --> 02:15:48,213\r\nJesus Christ, they change fast.\r\n\r\n810\r\n02:15:49,799 --> 02:15:52,426\r\nYeah, but he looks like my old man.\r\n\r\n811\r\n02:15:52,593 --> 02:15:54,469\r\nYeah, yeah, look, same eyes.\r\n\r\n812\r\n02:15:54,637 --> 02:15:57,014\r\nAnd look at that,\r\nthe same devilish pride, huh?\r\n\r\n813\r\n02:15:57,181 --> 02:16:00,058\r\nHey. Hey, hey.\r\n\r\n814\r\n02:16:00,226 --> 02:16:01,768\r\nDid you see his dickey?\r\n\r\n815\r\n02:16:01,936 --> 02:16:03,812\r\n- Vincent.\r\n- What?\r\n\r\n816\r\n02:16:03,980 --> 02:16:06,314\r\n- The girls.\r\n- The girls!\r\n\r\n817\r\n02:16:06,482 --> 02:16:12,404\r\nSooner or later you have to learn that\r\nafter me, the boss in the house is him.\r\n\r\n818\r\n02:16:12,572 --> 02:16:14,364\r\nHe's got balls just like his papa.\r\n\r\n819\r\n02:16:14,532 --> 02:16:15,782\r\n- Whoa! Hey!\r\n- Let me have him.\r\n\r\n820\r\n02:16:15,950 --> 02:16:19,578\r\nNo, no, no. I'll do this.\r\n\r\n821\r\n02:16:19,746 --> 02:16:21,621\r\nI'll do this, huh? Yeah.\r\n\r\n822\r\n02:16:24,959 --> 02:16:26,960\r\nLook. Hey, hey.\r\n\r\n823\r\n02:16:28,713 --> 02:16:31,131\r\nOoh. Ha-ha-ha.\r\n\r\n824\r\n02:16:31,632 --> 02:16:32,966\r\nLet Papa change you, huh?\r\n\r\n825\r\n02:16:33,134 --> 02:16:35,343\r\nCome on, look.\r\nGive me your little-bitty smile.\r\n\r\n826\r\n02:16:35,511 --> 02:16:40,390\r\nCome on, come on, come on.\r\n\r\n827\r\n02:16:41,768 --> 02:16:42,809\r\nWhat the fuck is this?\r\n\r\n828\r\n02:16:44,145 --> 02:16:49,316\r\n- What is this? Huh? What's that?\r\n- No! No! Oh, no!\r\n\r\n829\r\n02:16:49,859 --> 02:16:52,110\r\n- Look