n!\r\n\r\n600\r\n00:46:41,665 --> 00:46:45,931\r\n[Train Whistle Blowing]\r\n\r\n601\r\n00:46:47,938 --> 00:46:50,566\r\nStern!\nItzhak Stern!\r\n\r\n602\r\n00:46:50,641 --> 00:46:53,439\r\n[Kunfer, Tauber]\nStern.! Stern.!\nItzhak Stern.!\r\n\r\n603\r\n00:46:54,845 --> 00:46:56,073\r\nStern!\r\n\r\n604\r\n00:46:56,146 --> 00:46:58,080\r\nSir?\r\n\r\n605\r\n00:46:59,483 --> 00:47:02,452\r\nStern!\nHerr Direktor.\r\n\r\n606\r\n00:47:02,519 --> 00:47:05,386\r\n[Coughing]\nMy apologies.\r\n\r\n607\r\n00:47:05,455 --> 00:47:08,390\r\nStop the train!\nHe's here!\nI apologize.\r\n\r\n608\r\n00:47:08,458 --> 00:47:13,418\r\n- Stop the train!\n- Stop the train! Stop it!\r\n\r\n609\r\n00:47:25,976 --> 00:47:29,742\r\nSign here.\nInitial there.\n[Whistle Blowing]\r\n\r\n610\r\n00:47:29,813 --> 00:47:33,909\r\nMakes no difference\nto us, you understand.\nThis one, that one.\r\n\r\n611\r\n00:47:33,984 --> 00:47:36,578\r\n[Train Whistle Blowing]\nIt's the inconvenience\nto the list.\r\n\r\n612\r\n00:47:36,653 --> 00:47:40,419\r\nIt's the paperwork.\nI somehow left\nmy work card at home.\r\n\r\n613\r\n00:47:40,490 --> 00:47:44,256\r\nI tried to explain them\nit was a mistake, but...\r\n\r\n614\r\n00:47:44,328 --> 00:47:48,424\r\nI'm sorry, it was stupid!\nWhat if I got here\nfive minutes later?\r\n\r\n615\r\n00:47:48,498 --> 00:47:51,228\r\nThen where would I be?\r\n\r\n616\r\n00:49:31,802 --> 00:49:33,394\r\nShechel.\r\n\r\n617\r\n00:49:33,470 --> 00:49:36,337\r\nSacrean,\nsacrean enf tzukeer.\r\n\r\n618\r\n00:49:36,406 --> 00:49:38,966\r\nTzukeer enf sacrean.\r\n\r\n619\r\n00:49:42,679 --> 00:49:45,239\r\nI woke up from a dream\nthis morning.\r\n\r\n620\r\n00:49:45,315 --> 00:49:49,581\r\nI was broke and sharing a room\nwith 12 people I didn't know,\r\n\r\n621\r\n00:49:49,653 --> 00:49:54,920\r\nonly to discover\nI was broke and sharing a room\nwith 12 people I didn't know.\r\n\r\n622\r\n00:49:54,958 --> 00:49:55,925\r\n[Chuckling]\r\n\r\n623\r\n00:49:55,993 --> 00:49:58,427\r\nYou laugh about it?\nI have to laugh.\r\n\r\n624\r\n00:49:58,495 --> 00:50:01,430\r\nYou are living\nbehind walls.\r\n\r\n625\r\n00:50:01,465 --> 00:50:06,266\r\nThe walls I can feal with.\nIt's the restrictions\nto my life I'm tiref of.\r\n\r\n626\r\n00:50:06,336 --> 00:50:09,499\r\nThose walls keep them out.\nThat's all I care about.\r\n\r\n627\r\n00:50:09,539 --> 00:50:12,269\r\nI like it here.\nThere's a kind of,\nI don't know,\r\n\r\n628\r\n00:50:12,342 --> 00:50:14,640\r\nancestral squalor\nto it all.\r\n\r\n629\r\n00:50:14,711 --> 00:50:16,941\r\nYou are a slave\nto these people.\nNo one envies us anymore.\r\n\r\n630\r\n00:50:17,014 --> 00:50:19,107\r\nI'm smart.\nOh, yes,\nyou're smart.\r\n\r\n631\r\n00:50:19,182 --> 00:50:21,446\r\nYou're\na real genius.\nYou had your chance.\r\n\r\n632\r\n00:50:21,518 --> 00:50:26,251\r\nToday,\ntoday I actually found time\nto organize a thought.\r\n\r\n633\r\n00:50:26,323 --> 00:50:29,121\r\nI can't remember\nthe last time I did that.\r\n\r\n634\r\n00:50:29,192 --> 00:50:31,126\r\nWhen's the last time\nwe did this?\r\n\r\n635\r\n00:50:31,194 --> 00:50:33,594\r\nWhen's the last time\nwe stood around and talked?\r\n\r\n636\r\n00:50:33,663 --> 00:50:36,962\r\nNo one ordered me\nonto a truck today.\r\n\r\n637\r\n00:50:37,034 --> 00:50:39,332\r\nNo one took my business\naway from me.\r\n\r\n638\r\n00:50:39,403 --> 00:50:41,462\r\nYou don't really have\na business to take.\r\n\r\n639\r\n00:50:41,538 --> 00:50:43,802\r\nThere's nowhere\ndown from here.\r\n\r\n640\r\n00:50:43,874 --> 00:50:46,138\r\nThis is it.\nThis is the bottom.\r\n\r\n641\r\n00:50:46,209 --> 00:50:49,975\r\nThe ghetto is... liberty.\r\n\r\n642\r\n00:50:56,153 --> 00:50:59,486\r\nThis street\ndivides the ghetto\njust about in half.\r\n\r\n643\r\n00:50:59,556 --> 00:51:04,926\r\nRight side, Ghetto A:\nCivil employees,\r\n\r\n644\r\n00:51:04,995 --> 00:51:07,930\r\nindustrial workers\nand so on.\r\n\r\n645\r\n00:51:07,998 --> 00:51:12,935\r\nLeft side, Ghetto B