ols?\r\n\r\n707\r\n00:56:18,952 --> 00:56:19,589\r\nI don't know.\r\n\r\n708\r\n00:56:21,752 --> 00:56:23,982\r\nTell me what's\nreally bothering you.\r\n\r\n709\r\n00:56:26,872 --> 00:56:29,102\r\nDavid and I\nare going to have a baby.\r\n\r\n710\r\n00:56:33,793 --> 00:56:34,942\r\nTracy, I...\r\n\r\n711\r\n00:56:36,793 --> 00:56:38,021\r\nI don't think I'm...\r\n\r\n712\r\n00:56:38,753 --> 00:56:39,708\r\nthe one to talk to...\r\n\r\n713\r\n00:56:40,113 --> 00:56:42,707\r\n...about this.\n- I hate this city.\r\n\r\n714\r\n00:56:46,913 --> 00:56:48,744\r\nI had a relationship once.\r\n\r\n715\r\n00:56:49,433 --> 00:56:51,344\r\nIt was like a marriage.\r\n\r\n716\r\n00:56:54,354 --> 00:56:55,707\r\nWe got pregnant.\r\n\r\n717\r\n00:56:57,114 --> 00:56:58,945\r\nThis was a long time ago.\r\n\r\n718\r\n00:57:04,554 --> 00:57:07,671\r\nI remember getting up\nand going to work.\r\n\r\n719\r\n00:57:09,674 --> 00:57:13,633\r\nA day like any other,\nbut the first day after I knew\r\n\r\n720\r\n00:57:14,475 --> 00:57:15,271\r\nabout the pregnancy.\r\n\r\n721\r\n00:57:17,435 --> 00:57:19,312\r\nAnd I felt this fear,\r\n\r\n722\r\n00:57:20,315 --> 00:57:21,270\r\nfor the first time ever.\r\n\r\n723\r\n00:57:24,355 --> 00:57:25,629\r\nI remember thinking:\r\n\r\n724\r\n00:57:26,395 --> 00:57:29,432\r\nHow can I bring a child\ninto a world like this?\r\n\r\n725\r\n00:57:29,675 --> 00:57:32,553\r\nHow can a person grow up\nwith all this around them?\r\n\r\n726\r\n00:57:39,836 --> 00:57:41,747\r\nI told her I didn't want it.\r\n\r\n727\r\n00:57:44,076 --> 00:57:45,873\r\nOver the next few weeks,\r\n\r\n728\r\n00:57:47,116 --> 00:57:48,834\r\nI wore her down.\r\n\r\n729\r\n00:57:51,396 --> 00:57:53,193\r\nI want to have children.\r\n\r\n730\r\n00:57:57,796 --> 00:57:59,389\r\nI can tell you now that...\r\n\r\n731\r\n00:58:00,637 --> 00:58:02,548\r\nI know, I mean,\r\n\r\n732\r\n00:58:04,757 --> 00:58:05,985\r\nI'm positive that\r\n\r\n733\r\n00:58:06,637 --> 00:58:08,389\r\nI made the right decision.\r\n\r\n734\r\n00:58:09,157 --> 00:58:12,115\r\nBut not a day passes\nthat I don't wish\r\n\r\n735\r\n00:58:12,357 --> 00:58:14,917\r\nthat I'd made\na different choice.\r\n\r\n736\r\n00:58:18,317 --> 00:58:19,193\r\nIf you don't...\r\n\r\n737\r\n00:58:19,557 --> 00:58:20,229\r\nkeep the baby...\r\n\r\n738\r\n00:58:22,078 --> 00:58:25,036\r\nif that's your decision,\r\n\r\n739\r\n00:58:27,158 --> 00:58:29,547\r\ndon't ever tell him\nyou were pregnant.\r\n\r\n740\r\n00:58:31,198 --> 00:58:33,996\r\nBut if you choose to\nhave this baby,\r\n\r\n741\r\n00:58:34,798 --> 00:58:35,947\r\nthen spoil that kid,\r\n\r\n742\r\n00:58:36,198 --> 00:58:38,075\r\nevery chance you get.\r\n\r\n743\r\n00:58:44,599 --> 00:58:45,315\r\nThat's about...\r\n\r\n744\r\n00:58:45,599 --> 00:58:46,395\r\nall the advice\r\n\r\n745\r\n00:58:46,839 --> 00:58:48,795\r\nI can give you, Tracy.\r\n\r\n746\r\n00:58:55,999 --> 00:58:56,749\r\nI got to go.\r\n\r\n747\r\n00:58:57,839 --> 00:58:58,476\r\nWilliam,\r\n\r\n748\r\n00:59:05,960 --> 00:59:06,631\r\nthank you.\r\n\r\n749\r\n00:59:20,240 --> 00:59:21,434\r\nVictor's landlord said\r\n\r\n750\r\n00:59:21,680 --> 00:59:24,148\r\nthere was cash in the mailbox,\r\n\r\n751\r\n00:59:24,400 --> 00:59:25,880\r\nfirst of every month.\r\n\r\n752\r\n00:59:30,721 --> 00:59:31,278\r\nQuote:\r\n\r\n753\r\n00:59:32,081 --> 00:59:34,595\r\n\"I never heard a single complaint\nfrom the tenant...\r\n\r\n754\r\n00:59:34,841 --> 00:59:38,117\r\nin apartment 306,\nand nobody complained about him.\r\n\r\n755\r\n00:59:38,401 --> 00:59:40,153\r\nBest tenant I've ever had.\"\r\n\r\n756\r\n00:59:40,401 --> 00:59:42,278\r\nA landlord's dream.\r\n\r\n757\r\n00:59:42,481 --> 00:59:44,517\r\nA paralyzed tenant\nwith no tongue.\r\n\r\n758\r\n00:59:44,921 --> 00:59:46,320\r\nWho pays the rent on time.\r\n\r\n759\r\n00:59:47,281 --> 00:59:48,920\r\nI'm sick of this waiting.\r\n\r\n760\r\n00:59:49,122 --> 00:59:50,111\r\nThis is the job.\r\n\r\n761\r\n00:59:51,402 --> 00:59:53,074\r\nWhy aren't we out there?\r\n\r\n762\r\n00:59:53,282 --> 00:59:56,354\r\nWhy sit here rotting,\nwaiting till the lunatic\r\n\r\n763\r\n00:59:56,602 --> 00:59:57,751\r\ndoes it again?\r\n\r\n764\r\n00:59:58,082 --> 01:00:00,915\r\n\"Lunatic\" is dismissive.\nDon't make that mistake.\r\n\r\n765\r\n01:00:01,202 --> 01:00:03,511\r\nCome on. He's insane.\nLook.\r\n\r\n766\r\n01:00:03,762 --> 01:00:07,550\r\nRight now he's dancing\nin his grandma's panties.\r\n\r\n767\r\n01:00:07,802 --> 01:00:10,192\r\nRubbing himself in peanut butter.\r\n\r\n768\r\n01:00:10,963 --> 01:00:12,840\r\n- How's that?\n- I don't think so.\r\n\r\n769\r\n01:00:14,603 --> 01:00:16,434\r\nHis luck will run out.\r\n\r\n770\r\n01:00:17,643 --> 01:00:19,235\r\nHe's not depending on luck.\r\n\r\n771\r\n01:00:22,523 --> 01:00:26,311\r\nWe walk in exactly one year\nafter Victor's tied to the bed.\r\n\r\n772\r\n01:00:26,563 --> 01:00:27,882\r\nOne year to the day.\r\n\r\n773\r\n01:00:28,083 --> 01:00:30,597\r\n- He wanted us to.\n- Don't know that for sure.\r\n\r\n774\r\n01:00:30,803 --> 01:00:31,680\r\nOh, yes we do.\r\n\r\n775\r\n01:00:33,164 --> 01:00:36,793\r\nThe note he left,\nhis first words to us:\r\n\r\n776\r\n01:00:37,044 --> 01:00:39,399\r\n\"Long is the way and hard\nthat out of Hell\r\n\r\n777\r\n01:00:39,644 --> 01:00:41,555\r\nleads up to light.\"\r\n\r\n778\r\n01:00:43,044 --> 01:00:44,363\r\nFuck him. So what?\r\n\r\n779\r\n01:00:44,644 --> 01:00:45,918\r\nHe's right so far.\r\n\r\n780\r\n01:00:46,484 --> 01:00:50,272\r\nImagine the will to keep\na man bound for a year.\r\n\r\n781\r\n01:00:50,844 --> 01:00:52,995\r\nTo sever his hand\nand to use it...\r\n\r\n782\r\n01:00:53,245 --> 01:00:54,724\r\nto plant fingerprints.\r\n\r\n783\r\n01:00:54,965 --> 01:00:57,274\r\nTo insert tubes into\nhis genitals.\r\n\r\n784\r\n01:00:57,965 --> 01:01:00,354\r\nThe guy's methodical, exacting\r\n\r\n785\r\n01:01:00,605 --> 01:01:02,482\r\nand worst of all, patient.\r\n\r\n786\r\n01:01:02,885 --> 01:01:04,364\r\nHe's a nutbag.\r\n\r\n787\r\n01:01:04,645 --> 01:01:08,160\r\nBecause he's got a library card\ndoesn't make him Yoda.\r\n\r\n788\r\n01:01:12,925 --> 01:01:13,835\r\nYou got money?\r\n\r\n789\r\n01:01:14,565 --> 01:01:16,045\r\nI got 50 bucks.\r\n\r\n790\r\n01:01:16,366 --> 01:01:18,436\r\nI propose a field trip.\nCome on.\r\n\r\n791\r\n01:01:22,246 --> 01:01:24,840\r\nWe'll make a list.\nAt the top we put \"Purgatory\",\r\n\r\n792\r\n01:01:25,126 --> 01:01:28,755\r\n\"Canterbury Tales\"\nanything on the 7 deadly sins.\r\n\r\n793\r\n01:01:29,046 --> 01:01:30,274\r\n- Ask yourself.\n- Wait.\r\n\r\n794\r\n01:01:30,486 --> 01:01:33,159\r\nWhat would he study\nto do things he's done?\r\n\r\n795\r\n01:01:33,406 --> 01:01:34,885\r\nWhat are his interests now?\r\n\r\n796\r\n01:01:35,686 --> 01:01:37,643\r\nJack the Ripper, for instance.\r\n\r\n797\r\n01:01:37,887 --> 01:01:39,400\r\n- Where are we going?\n- Library.\r\n\r\n798\r\n01:01:52,967 --> 01:01:55,527\r\nCoupons!\nFree coupons!\r\n\r\n799\r\n01:01:55,767 --> 01:01:57,086\r\nDiscount coupons!\r\n\r\n800\r\n01:01:58,407 --> 01:02:00,444\r\nThey must have had\nabout 50 health violations\r\n\r\n801\r\n01:02:00,648 --> 01:02:02,764\r\nduring the last inspection.\r\n\r\n802\r\n01:02:03,008 --> 01:02:05,602\r\nSit across from me.\nI don't want people thinking\r\n\r\n803\r\n01:02:05,808 --> 01:02:07,036\r\nwe're dating.\r\n\r\n804\r\n01:02:07,528 --> 01:02:08,438\r\nGive me your money.\r\n\r\n805\r\n01:02:10,368 --> 01:02:14,077\r\nI'll give you this,\nbut I must know what we're doing.\r\n\r\n806\r\n01:02:19,208 --> 01:02:20,801\r\nSomerset. How you doing?\r\n\r\n807\r\n01:02:21,129 --> 01:02:23,643\r\nDidn't expect a ménage á trois.\r\n\r\n808\r\n01:02:23,889 --> 01:02:25,766\r\nIt's not a problem. Sit down.\r\n\r\n809\r\n01:02:31,169 --> 01:02:33,967\r\nOnly for you do I do this.\nIt's a big risk.\r\n\r\n810\r\n01:02:34,329 --> 01:02:37,321\r\n- We're just fair and square.\n- It's a deal.\r\n\r\n811\r\n01:02:42,610 --> 01:02:43,884\r\nAbout an hour.\r\n\r\n812\r\n01:02:46,010 --> 01:02:47,329\r\nYeah. Help yourself.\r\n\r\n813\r\n01:02:50,170 --> 01:02:51,842\r\nThat was money well spent.\r\n\r\n814\r\n01:02:53,170 --> 01:02:53,647\r\nYeah.\r\n\r\n815\r\n01:02:54,305 --> 01:03:00,585\r\nBest watched using Open Subtitles MKV Player\r\n\r\n","markerStore":{"nextMarkerId":24,"markersById":{"0":{"range":{"start":{"row":1743,"column":0},"end":{"row":1743,"column":8}},"properties":{"type":"selection","editorId":92,"goalScreenRange":null},"reversed":false,"tailed":true,"valid":true,"invalidate":"never","maintainHistory":true}},"version":2},"history":{"version":3,"nextCheckpointId":1,"undoStack":[],"redoStack":[]},"encoding":"utf8","filePath":"/Users/joegesualdo/.Trash/Se7en (1995).en.srt 2.14.37 PM","digestWhenLastPersisted":"d6a8506afe628998062044bfe00c169b5592fa47","preferredLineEnding":null,"deserializer":"TextBuffer","version":2},{"load":true,"text":"       ÜÛÛÛÛßÛÜ             ÜÛÛÛÛßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßßÛ\r\n     ÜÛßÛÛß   ßÛÜ         ÜÛÛÛÛß                                               Û\r\n   ÜÛÛÛÛß       ßÛÜ     ÜÛÛÜÛß                                                 Û\r\n ÜÛÛÛÛß           ßÛÜ ÜÛÛÛÛß                                                   Û\r\nÛÛÜÛß               ÛÛÛÛÛß                                                     Û\r\nÛÛßÛÜ             ÜÛÛÜÛß                                                       Û\r\nß   ßÛÜ         ÜÛÛÛÛß                                                         Û\r\n      ßÛÜ     ÜÛßÛÛß                                                           Û\r\n        ßÛÜ ÜÛÛÛÛß                                                             Û\r\n          ÛÛÛÛÛß                             Û     Û     Û  Û                  Û\r\n        ÜÛÛÜÛß  ÜÜ  ÜÜÜ   ÜÜ  ÜÜÜ   ÜÜÜ Ü  Ü ÛÜÜ  ÜÛÜ ß ÜÛÜ Û  ÜÜ   ÜÜÜ        Û\r\n      ÜÛÛÛÛß   Û  Û Û  Û Û  Û Û  Û ÛÜÜÜ Û  Û Û  Û  Û  Û  Û  Û Û  Û ÛÜÜÜ        Û\r\n    ÜÛßÛÛß     